            the two if and only if 'DLA Inspired' is plugged in a direct \
            colouring. If plugged into a gradient colouring then the \
            'Combined' option is ignored and 'Colour' used instead."
    visible = @numplants>6
  endparam
  float param palmin8
    caption = "Min. Palette Index"
    default = 0.0
    min = 0.0
    max = 399.0
